File:Manjumori Kofun, genshitsu-2.jpg|Main chamber, view towards entrance
File:Manjumori Kofun, sendou-2.jpg|Passage, view towards entrance
File:Manjumori Kofun, sendou-1.jpg|Passage, view towards main chamber
File:Manjumori Kofun, entrance.jpg|Entrance
File:Manjumori Kofun Aug. 2015.JPG|Kofun and stone chamber entrance (2015)
</gallery>

